title: The Black Lodge
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: A Twin Peaks TV show themed vegetarian food restaurant, est. Jun 2013. Serves casual, pub food. The bar uses non-veg items like Clamato which is made with clam juice as well regular Worcestershire sauce and marshallow which are not vegetarian. Vegan options are upon request and in some cases might cost extra.
